Dataset source: 
IEEE DataPort - Fine-Grained Balanced Cyberbullying Dataset (2021) 
Type: 
Textual dataset (English-language tweets) 
Instances: 48,000 tweets 
Features: 
•	Tweet text (raw textual content) 
•	Label (type of cyberbullying) 
Target Variable: 
Cyberbullying category (multi-class classification with six classes) 
Class Labels: 
•	Age-based cyberbullying 
•	Ethnicity-based cyberbullying 
•	Gender-based cyberbullying 
•	Religion-based cyberbullying 
•	Other/general harassment 
•	Not cyberbullying 

Class Distribution: 
Perfectly balanced dataset with 8,000 instances per class 
 Missing Values: 
No missing values reported 

